{
  "info": {
    "name": "Picking App - Warehouse Flexxus Credentials",
    "description": "Colección completa para testear el sistema de credenciales Flexxus por depósito. Incluye endpoints de autenticación, gestión de credenciales (admin), picking (operarios) y override de depósito.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.1.0"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "01 - Auth - Login (Admin)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/api/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
          "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "Login como administrador para obtener token Sanctum.\n\n**Credenciales por defecto en seeders:**\n- Username: admin\n- Password: password\n\n**Tests validados:**\n- Status 200\n- Token devuelto\n- Usuario con rol admin\n- Tiene permiso can_override_warehouse"
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Test: Login exitoso",
              "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Test: Respuesta contiene token",
              "pm.test(\"Response has token\", function () {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.have.property('token');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Test: Usuario es admin",
              "pm.test(\"User is admin\", function () {",
              "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.user.role).to.eql('admin');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Guardar token para próximos requests",
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"admin_token\", jsonData.token);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"admin_id\", jsonData.user.id);",
              "",
              "// Test: Admin puede override warehouse",
              "pm.test(\"Admin can override warehouse\", function () {",
              "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.user.can_override_warehouse).to.eql(true);",
              "});"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "02 - Auth - Login (Operario Rondeau)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"operador_rondeau\",\n  \"password\": \"password\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/api/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
          "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
        },
        "description": "Login como operario asignado a Rondeau (depósito 002).\n\n**Credenciales:**\n- Username: operador_rondeau (o cualquier operario con warehouse_id = 2)\n- Password: password\n\n**Tests validados:**\n- Status 200\n- Token devuelto\n- Usuario tiene warehouse asignado\n- Warehouse code es 002"
      },
      "response": [],
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "// Test: Login exitoso",
              "pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Test: Usuario tiene warehouse asignado",
              "pm.test(\"User has warehouse assigned\", function () {",
              "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.user).to.have.property('warehouse');",
              "});",
              "",
              "// Guardar token",
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"operador_token\", jsonData.token);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"operador_id\", jsonData.user.id);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"warehouse_002_id\", jsonData.user.warehouse.id);",
              "",
              "// Test: Warehouse code es 002 (Rondeau)",
              "pm.test(\"Warehouse code is 002 (Rondeau)\", function () {",
              "    const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.user.warehouse.code).to.eql('002');",
              "});"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
